    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute favorite ride, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! It\u2019s in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless, so it\u2019s ready for all your adventures with zero worries. You\u2019ve seriously gotta see it in person to believe how clean it is! Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look\u2014I'd love to find it a great new home!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
