      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a collector-grade example of the legendary S65B40 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. Engineering highlights include eight individual throttle bodies and a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a factory carbon fiber roof to optimize the center of gravity. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement with treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The finish remains impeccable with zero rock chips or bolster wear, reflecting its pristine mechanical and cosmetic state. A true purist's specification with absolute structural and drivetrain integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
