    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition and meticulously maintained by a single dedicated owner. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no door dings, rock chips, or swirl marks to be found on the bodywork. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original floor mats look untouched. All interior electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function with factory-new precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garaged in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a complete, organized folder of service records included. The engine bay is spotless, and the vehicle drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a brand-new car. Currently fitted with a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires, this is an investment-grade example suited for the most discerning collector who demands perfection.",
